name: Confront
description:
this is the second series of the theme entitled "a fraction of a second"
This idea arises when how sometimes we are stuck in a decision that must be taken at the same time and in the same space and in a matter of seconds you have to make that decision. I Create several works with different compositional structures, but still in the same space changing the order and interpretation. this is my interpretation of "a fraction of a second"
